1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,200
Here's what science actually says about meta-analysis basics.

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:06,800
Meta-analysis combines results from different studies to find patterns.

3
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:09,200
Think of it as pooling knowledge!

4
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:11,200
But why is this important?

5
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:14,800
It helps us see the bigger picture in research.

6
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:21,200
Research shows that meta-analyses can provide more reliable conclusions than single studies, especially in complex fields.

7
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:24,000
However, not all meta-analyses are created equal.

8
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:27,200
Always check the quality of the studies included.

9
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:29,200
